<div type="content">
<ab>Wir, die <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> etc., bekennen etc. umb sölich
                        tawsent <expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> gut new ungrisch
                                <expan>guld<ex>en,</ex></expan> die uns von dem
                                <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n,</expan> vesten
                            <expan>ritt<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>Rosemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> und
                        frawn <expan>Elspet<ex>en</ex></expan> Marschelkin von Pappenheim,
                                <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>elich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wirtin<ex>n,</ex></expan> von der <expan>jerlich<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        gült <expan>weg<ex>en,</ex></expan> die sie uns ausz dem sloss, veste und
                        stat Hilpolstein zu <expan>kawff<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hett<ex>en</ex></expan>, noch unbeczalt auszsteen über die zwey
                        tawsent gut new ungrisch <expan>guld<ex>en,</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> uns vor von iren
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> ein <expan>v<ex>er</ex>weisung</expan> und
                        ein <expan>genüg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>bescheh<ex>en</ex></expan> ist, daz uns der hochgeborn furst und
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Lud<ex>wig,</ex></expan> pfallnczgraf bey Reyn,
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan> in Peyern und graf zu Mortani etc.,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re,</expan> der <expan>vorges<ex>chriben</ex></expan> m
                                <expan>gut<ex>er</ex></expan> newr
                            <expan>ungrisch<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> von der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>Rosemb<ex>er</ex>gs</expan> und
                        frawn <expan>Elspet<ex>en,</ex></expan>
<expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan>
<pb facs="#facs_284" id="142r"/>
<expan>elich<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>wirtin<ex>n,</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>weiset</expan> hat an den <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n,</expan>
                        vesten Heymran Nothaft zu <expan>Wermb<ex>er</ex>g,</expan>
<expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> zum Bargstein, und an die
                                <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> des rats und der stat
                                <expan>gemeinl<ex>ich</ex></expan> zu der Weyden, uns die auf <app>
<note><q type="date">sand Michelstag schierist
                                künftig</q>29.09.1416</note>
</app> zu beczaln nach lawt und sag des briefs, den sie uns
                                <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> besigelt und
                            <expan>gegeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> so
                                <expan>sag<ex>en</ex></expan> wir den
                            <expan>obg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren,</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
<expan>Ludweig<ex>en,</ex></expan> und auch die
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>Rosemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, frawn
                                <expan>Elspet<ex>en,</ex></expan> sein elich
                            <expan>wirtin<ex>n</ex></expan>, und ir <expan>erb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        der <expan>eges<ex>chriben</ex></expan> m <expan>new<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ungrisch<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> für uns und <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>nachkom<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan> quitt, ledig und lose, doch
                                <expan>unschedl<ex>ich</ex></expan> uns und
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>nachkom<ex>en</ex></expan> an <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> brief
                        und <expan>bürg<ex>en,</ex></expan> die wir von den
                                <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>Heymra<ex>n</ex></expan> Nothaft und der stat zu der
                                <expan>Weyde<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, als <expan>vorges<ex>chriben</ex></expan>
                        stett. Mit <expan>urk<ex>unde</ex></expan> dicz
                            <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>sigelt</expan> a tergo. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>palma<ex>rum</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
